Class Reporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • Reporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientReporter, ManagerReporter, ProfessionalReporter
    public abstract class Reporter
extends java.lang.Object
    Reporter is an abstract Reporter class. All specific Reporters depend on the methods defined in this superclass, and thus inherit from it.

      • getWeekPrice

        public static double getWeekPrice​(Activity a)
        Returns the price of the week. This "price of the week" is the combined price of the activity for the week. If the activity is not pay-per-client, we count the number of times it happened during the week, and add price * [that number] into the total. Otherwise, we look at all the attendances for the activity for the week, and we add price * [number of attendances] to the total.
        Parameters:
        a - the activity
        Returns:
        the price of the activity for the week

      • getWeekPrice

        public static double getWeekPrice​(java.util.ArrayList<Activity> list)
        Calls getWeekPrice on every activity in a list, and adds their totals together
        Parameters:
        list - the list of activities
        Returns:
        the total combined price of the activities for the week
